----------
TUTORIAL 4
----------

This is an introduction to bare-metal programming on Raspberry Pi using
C language. This module creates a program that simply echoes whatever
byte that is detected on the incoming UART line.

---------
Objective
---------

----------
Background
----------

--------
Contents
--------

As usual the new uart module is written as 'uart.c' and 'uart.h'. The gpio
module is rewritten to include a feature to change pull-{up,down} settings
of a GPIO pin.

